-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 1em;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 1em;margin-left: 0;padding-top: 0;padding-right: 0;padding-bottom: 0;padding-left: 0;vertical-align: top;word-wrap: break-word;"><strong>Workshop ''Maak een kleurrijke dromenvanger!''</strong></p><p style="font-family: Arial, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;color: #000000;color: #000000 !important;background-color: #FFFFFF;border: 0;letter-spacing: normal;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 1em;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 1em;margin-left: 0;padding-top: 0;padding-right: 0;padding-bottom: 0;padding-left: 0;vertical-align: top;word-wrap: break-word;">Maak je eigen mooie dromenvanger voor in je huis of om iemand cadeau te geven én kom<br style="border: 0;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;padding-top: 0;padding-right: 0;padding-bottom: 0;padding-left: 0;">meer te weten over de betekenis van de kleuren in jouw dromen! <br style="border: 0;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;padding-top: 0;padding-right: 0;padding-bottom: 0;padding-left: 0;"><br style="border: 0;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;padding-top: 0;padding-right: 0;padding-bottom: 0;padding-left: 0;"><strong>Wanneer:</strong> Dinsdag 18 oktober, 20.00 – 22.00 uur,<br style="border: 0;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;padding-top: 0;padding-right: 0;padding-bottom: 0;padding-left: 0;"><strong>Waar:</strong> Buurt Ontmoetings Plaats (BOP) Herenstraat 61, Leiden. <br style="border: 0;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;padding-top: 0;padding-right: 0;padding-bottom: 0;padding-left: 0;"><strong>Kosten:</strong> €17,50 incl. materiaal, kleurenkennis en heerlijke kleuren- kruidenthee.</p><p style="font-family: Arial, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;color: #000000;color: #000000 !important;background-color: #FFFFFF;border: 0;letter-spacing: normal;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 1em;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 1em;margin-left: 0;padding-top: 0;padding-right: 0;padding-bottom: 0;padding-left: 0;vertical-align: top;word-wrap: break-word;"><em>P.S. Heb je schoolgaande kinderen? Meld je dan gratis aan bij de vakantiepas Leiden (<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial;"><a style="color: #4a91b0;color: #4a91b0 !important;background-color: #FFFFFF;text-decoration: none;border: 0;word-wrap: break-word;" href="https://www.vakantiepas.nl/vakantiepasclub/">https://www.vakantiepas.nl/vakantiepasclub/</a></span>). In de herfstvakantie geef ik speciaal voor&nbsp;kinderen een workshop ‘Dromenvanger maken’&nbsp;voor maar €7,50 op woensdag 19 oktober van 14.00 - 16.00 uur.</em></p><p style="font-family: Arial, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;color: #000000;color: #000000 !important;background-color: #FFFFFF;border: 0;letter-spacing: normal;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 1em;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 1em;margin-left: 0;padding-top: 0;padding-right: 0;padding-bottom: 0;padding-left: 0;vertical-align: top;word-wrap: break-word;"><strong>Workshop ''Schilder jouw krukje in jouw kleuren!''</strong></p><p style="font-family: Arial, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;color: #000000;color: #000000 !important;background-color: #FFFFFF;border: 0;letter-spacing: normal;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 1em;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 1em;margin-left: 0;padding-top: 0;padding-right: 0;padding-bottom: 0;padding-left: 0;vertical-align: top;word-wrap: break-word;">Welke kleuren heb jij in je huis? Welke kleuren heb jij nodig om je helemaal thuis en veilig te voelen? Kom naar deze workshop en schilder je eigen krukje in jouw kleuren! We werken met Milk Paint verf, hiermee kun je strak schilderen, maar ook juist een chippy look creëren. <br style="border: 0;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;padding-top: 0;padding-right: 0;padding-bottom: 0;padding-left: 0;"><br style="border: 0;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;padding-top: 0;padding-right: 0;padding-bottom: 0;padding-left: 0;"><strong>Wanneer:</strong> Dinsdag 15 november, 19.00 – 22.00 uur<br style="border: 0;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;padding-top: 0;padding-right: 0;padding-bottom: 0;padding-left: 0;"><strong>Waar:</strong> Locatie nog nader te bepalen.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br style="border: 0;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;padding-top: 0;padding-right: 0;padding-bottom: 0;padding-left: 0;"> <strong>Kosten:</strong> €35,00 incl. materiaal (krukje en Milk Paint verf), kleurenkennis en heerlijke kleuren- kruidenthee.</p><p style="font-family: Arial, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;color: #000000;color: #000000 !important;background-color: #FFFFFF;border: 0;letter-spacing: normal;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 150%;margin-top: 1em;margin-right: 0;margin-botto